---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
export const prerender = true;
---

<Base
  title="Terms & Conditions — Activ365"
  description="Activ365 Terms & Conditions — free app, no warranties, your data stays on your device."
>
  <style>
    .legal-hero { padding: 80px 0 40px; }
    .legal-body {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 20px 100px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      line-height: 1.75;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    .legal-body h2 {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text);
      margin: 40px 0 12px;
    }
    .legal-body h3 {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text);
      margin: 28px 0 8px;
    }
    .legal-body p { margin: 0 0 14px; }
    .legal-body ul { margin: 0 0 14px; padding-left: 22px; }
    .legal-body ul li { margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .legal-body a { color: #34d399; text-decoration: none; }
    .legal-body a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    .legal-back {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .legal-back:hover { color: #34d399; }
    .app-tag {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #34d399;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
  </style>

  <section class="legal-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/activ365" class="legal-back">
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M19 12H5M12 5l-7 7 7 7"/></svg>
        Activ365
      </a>
      <div class="app-tag">
        <span>✅</span> ACTIV365
      </div>
      <h1 style="font-size:clamp(32px,5vw,56px);margin-bottom:12px;">Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
      <p style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:15px;">Last updated: 20 April 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="legal-body">

    <h2>1. Agreement to Terms</h2>
    <p>
      By downloading or using Activ365 ("the App"), you agree to be bound by these Terms and
      Conditions. If you do not agree, do not use the App. These terms are governed by the
      laws of New South Wales, Australia.
    </p>
    <p>
      The App is published by Nano Synapsys ("we", "us", "our"), based in Australia.
      Contact: <a href="mailto:support@nano-synapsys.com">support@nano-synapsys.com</a>
    </p>

    <h2>2. Licence to Use</h2>
    <p>
      We grant you a personal, non-exclusive, non-transferable, revocable licence to use
      the App on any Apple device you own or control, subject to these Terms and the Apple
      App Store Terms of Service.
    </p>
    <p>You may not:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Copy, modify, or distribute the App or its content</li>
      <li>Reverse-engineer or attempt to extract the source code</li>
      <li>Use the App for any commercial purpose without our written consent</li>
      <li>Remove any copyright or proprietary notices</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Free App — No Subscription</h2>
    <p>
      Activ365 is provided free of charge. There are no in-app purchases, subscriptions,
      or premium tiers. We reserve the right to introduce optional paid features in a future
      version; any such changes will be clearly communicated before they take effect.
    </p>

    <h2>4. Your Data</h2>
    <p>
      All workout data, goals, and preferences you enter into the App are stored exclusively
      on your device. We have no access to this data. You are solely responsible for backing
      up and managing your data. Uninstalling the App permanently deletes all locally stored data.
    </p>
    <p>
      See our <a href="/activ365/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> for full details on data handling.
    </p>

    <h2>5. Accuracy of Information</h2>
    <p>
      Activ365 is a personal tracking tool. It is not a medical device and does not provide
      health, medical, or fitness advice. The goal-tracking and workout-logging features are
      for motivational and organisational purposes only. Always consult a qualified health
      professional before beginning any exercise programme.
    </p>

    <h2>6. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
    <p>
      The App is provided "as is" and "as available" without warranties of any kind, express
      or implied, including but not limited to implied warranties of merchantability, fitness
      for a particular purpose, and non-infringement.
    </p>
    <p>
      We do not warrant that the App will be error-free, uninterrupted, or free of viruses
      or other harmful components.
    </p>

    <h2>7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
    <p>
      To the maximum extent permitted by applicable law, Nano Synapsys shall not be liable
      for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising from
      your use of, or inability to use, the App — including loss of data.
    </p>
    <p>
      Our total liability to you for any claim arising out of or relating to these Terms or
      the App shall not exceed AUD $10.
    </p>

    <h2>8. Intellectual Property</h2>
    <p>
      All intellectual property rights in the App — including its design, code, branding,
      and content — are owned by or licensed to Nano Synapsys. Nothing in these Terms
      transfers any intellectual property rights to you.
    </p>

    <h2>9. Updates and Modifications</h2>
    <p>
      We may update the App at any time to add features, fix bugs, or address security issues.
      We may also modify these Terms at any time. The "Last updated" date at the top of this
      page reflects the most recent revision. Continued use of the App after changes constitutes
      acceptance of the updated Terms.
    </p>

    <h2>10. Termination</h2>
    <p>
      We reserve the right to discontinue the App at any time without notice. You may stop
      using the App at any time by deleting it from your device.
    </p>

    <h2>11. Third-Party Terms</h2>
    <p>
      The App is distributed via the Apple App Store. Your use is also subject to Apple's
      <a href="https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Standard End User Licence Agreement (EULA)</a>.
      Apple is a third-party beneficiary of these Terms and has the right to enforce them.
    </p>

    <h2>12. Governing Law</h2>
    <p>
      These Terms are governed by the laws of New South Wales, Australia. Any disputes
      shall be resolved in the courts of New South Wales, and you consent to the exclusive
      jurisdiction of those courts.
    </p>

    <h2>13. Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Questions about these Terms?<br />
      <a href="mailto:support@nano-synapsys.com">support@nano-synapsys.com</a>
    </p>

    <p style="margin-top:48px;padding-top:24px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);">
      <a href="/activ365/privacy">Privacy Policy →</a> &nbsp;·&nbsp;
      <a href="/activ365">Back to Activ365</a> &nbsp;·&nbsp;
      <a href="/">Nano Synapsys</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</Base>
